金木犀の匂いがした
I smelled the scent of osmanthus.

15
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:36,500
明日のことも忘れたくなった
I wanted to forget about tomorrow, too.

16
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:40,800
いっそ逃げてしまおうかな
Maybe I should just run away instead.

17
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:45,300
僕は悲劇の主人公だ
I am the protagonist of a tragedy.

18
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:49,300
やさしいヒトで居たいな
I want to be a kind person.

19
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:53,900
でもそんな思いも偽善だ
But even that thought is hypocrisy.

20
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:57,900
誰も幸せにできないの
I can't make anyone happy.

21
00:04:57,900 --> 00:05:01,400
都合良いね、涙が出るの
How convenient, the tears are falling.

22
00:05:03,408 --> 00:05:07,508
ああ　どれだけ歌っても
Ah, no matter how much I sing,

23
00:05:07,508 --> 00:05:11,508
この声は君には届かない
This voice won't reach you.

24
00:05:11,508 --> 00:05:15,608
ああ　どれだけ歌っても
Ah, no matter how much I sing,

25
00:05:15,608 --> 00:05:19,608
この声は君には届かない
This voice won't reach you.

26
00:05:20,008 --> 00:05:24,208
ああ　息が苦しくなる
Ah, it's getting hard to breathe,

27
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:28,508
この歌もいつしか終わりが来る
This song, too, will eventually come to an end.

28
00:05:28,508 --> 00:05:32,708
ああ　息が苦しくなる
Ah, it's getting hard to breathe,

29
00:05:32,708 --> 00:05:37,008
この地球もいつかは終わりが来る
This planet, too, will eventually come to an end.

30
00:05:45,508 --> 00:05:49,308
金木犀の匂いをまた
The scent of osmanthus once again...

31
00:05:49,308 --> 00:05:53,508
思い出した
I remembered.

32
00:05:59,008 --> 00:06:01,008
In the dusk,

33
00:06:01,008 --> 00:06:02,608
amid the wintry wind...

34
00:06:02,608 --> 00:06:04,108
The shadow of a girl...

35
00:06:04,108 --> 00:06:06,308
Suddenly, the prologue begins.

36
00:06:06,508 --> 00:06:10,208
気付けば…駆けだしていた…
Before I knew it... I was running...

37
00:06:10,208 --> 00:06:13,808
揺れ動く…心のままに…
Following... my swaying heart...

38
00:06:13,808 --> 00:06:17,608
遠ざかる…白い壁…
Fading away... the white wall...

39
00:06:17,608 --> 00:06:21,408
一度も…振り返らずに…
Without... looking back once...

40
00:06:21,408 --> 00:06:25,108
《生命》が…消え逝く季節の…
In the season... where life fades away...

41
00:06:25,108 --> 00:06:28,808
胸を刺す…気配の中で…
Amidst the feeling... that pierces my chest...

42
00:06:28,808 --> 00:06:32,508
迫りくる…暗闇…
The approaching... darkness...

43
00:06:32,508 --> 00:06:36,208
二度と…明けぬような気がして…
Feeling like... it would never dawn again...

44
00:06:36,208 --> 00:06:39,808
転がり落ちそうな心
A heart that seemed like it would roll and fall,

45
00:06:39,808 --> 00:06:43,508
必死に抱き止めていた…
I was desperately holding onto it...

46
00:06:43,508 --> 00:06:48,008
星空へと続く長い坂道は
Because the long slope leading to the starry sky,

47
00:06:48,008 --> 00:06:52,808
永遠にも…思えたから――
Seemed... even like eternity—

48
00:06:52,808 --> 00:06:56,608
咲く花や…散りぬるを…
The flowers that bloom... and fall...

49
00:06:56,608 --> 00:07:00,508
神代の《時代》より繰り返す…
Repeating since the age of the gods...

50
00:07:00,508 --> 00:07:04,108
私はそれを…美しいとは…
I have never... thought of that...

51
00:07:04,108 --> 00:07:07,808
思ったことがない…
as being beautiful...

52
00:07:07,808 --> 00:07:12,008
久方の…春の陽を…
Scramble for the long-awaited spring sunlight,

53
00:07:12,008 --> 00:07:16,308
仮初めの影が奪い合う…
scrambled for by transient shadows...

54
00:07:16,308 --> 00:07:20,008
その営みを…美しいとは…
I have never... thought of that way of life...

55
00:07:20,008 --> 00:07:23,508
思ったことがない…
as being beautiful...

56
00:07:23,508 --> 00:07:27,808
諦めながら…生きてた…
I lived... while giving up...

57
00:07:27,808 --> 00:07:32,408
何も望まないように　それでも…
Trying not to wish for anything, and yet...

58
00:07:32,408 --> 00:07:36,008
手放せなかった…最後の願いを…
I couldn't let go... Grasping my last wish,

59
00:07:36,008 --> 00:07:39,008
握りしめて駆け上がる
I run up.

